OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FA judge on Wednesday reserved his
OL,7,Fverdict in the case of a retired
OL,8,FBaptist pastor who is accused of
OL,9,Fconducting an illegal abortion protest
OL,10,Finside the limits of a "safe access
OL,11,Fzone."
OL,13,FHaving heard the evidence in the case
OL,14,Fagainst Clive Johnston last month,
OL,15,Fcounsel for the prosecution and
OL,16,Fdefence supplemented their skeleton
OL,17,Farguments before District Judge Peter
OL,18,FKing.
OL,26,@rD@XOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FJudge King told the lawyer he was
OL,7,F"incredibly indebted" to the legal
OL,8,Fteams for their approach to the case.
OL,10,FHe added: "I don't think it would be
OL,11,Ffair to Mr. Johnson, or to be
OL,12,Frespectful to either of the legal
OL,13,Fteams in this case, if I were to
OL,14,Fextemporise today."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]rD@KOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FMr Johnston, from the Melmount Road in
OL,7,FSion Mills and who is a former
OL,8,FPresident of the Association of
OL,9,FBaptist Churches in Ireland, faces two
OL,10,Foffences under the Abortion Services
OL,11,F(Safe Access Zones) Act (Northern
OL,12,FIreland) 2023.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FThe 77-year-old retired pastor is
OL,7,Faccused of doing an act in a safe
OL,8,Faccess zone at the Causeway Hospital
OL,9,Fin Coleraine, "namely conducted a
OL,10,Fprotest with the intent of, or being
OL,11,Freckless as to whether, it had the
OL,12,Feffect of influencing a protected
OL,13,Fperson whether directly or indirectly,
OL,14,Fin connection with the protected
OL,15,Fperson attending the premises," on 7
OL,16,FJuly last year.
OL,18,FThe pensioner is further charged that
OL,19,Fon the same date he "failed to comply
OL,20,Fwith a direction...to leave a safe
OL,21,Faccess zone."
OL,26,@qD@OOUwD@_O]{D@UOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FUnder The Abortion Services (Safe
OL,7,FAccess Zones) Act (Northern Ireland)
OL,8,F2023, which received Royal Assent on 6
OL,9,FFebruary 2023, anti-abortion protests
OL,10,Fand other behaviours are prohibited
OL,11,Fwithin any Safe Access Zone once it
OL,12,Fhas been established, and this may be
OL,13,Fenforced by the PSNI.
OL,15,FIt is the prosecution case that the
OL,16,Fdefendant either intended to
OL,17,Finfluence, or was reckless as to
OL,18,Fwhether any "protected person"
OL,19,Fattending the Causeway Hospital
OL,20,Fabortion services, would be influenced.
OL,26,@zD@MOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FThe court has heard evidence, and been
OL,7,Fable to watch footage from police body
OL,8,Fworn cameras, that the retired pastor,
OL,9,Fstanding close to a large crucifix,
OL,10,Fwas using a microphone as he quoted
OL,11,Fpassages from the Bible.
OL,13,F"We are giving the word of God," Mr
OL,14,FJohnston is heard telling a police
OL,15,Finspector, "I want the Government to
OL,16,Fknow that there is a higher law."
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@`O]wD@LOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FGiving evidence on his own behalf, the
OL,7,F77-year-old maintained that although
OL,8,Fhe had objections to the laws which
OL,9,Fextended abortion services to NI, he
OL,10,Fwas not protesting outside the
OL,11,Fhospital on 7 July last year but
OL,12,Frather, he was giving a sermon and
OL,13,Fspreading the Gospel.
OL,15,FHe lamented that if it has come to a
OL,16,Fstage where spreading the "light of
OL,17,FJesus" is not allowed and is now
OL,18,Fillegal, "then in our country we have
OL,19,Fcome to a very sad position."
OL,26,@xD@[OUyD@FO]zD@JOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FIn court on Wednesday, prosecuting
OL,7,Fcounsel David McNeill submitted that
OL,8,Fthe offence is made out given the
OL,9,Fcontext, the location, the cross being
OL,10,Fpresent and that the group were
OL,11,Fsinging gospel songs.
OL,13,FThe purpose was not to conduct a
OL,14,Freligious service but rather the
OL,15,Fmessage was a "pro-life, anti abortion
OL,16,Fone," the barrister contended.
OL,26,@wD@OOUxD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FHe told the court he wanted to make it
OL,7,F"very clear... there is no prohibition
OL,8,Fon holding a religious service, except
OL,9,Fby the legislation in this very
OL,10,Flimited location."
OL,12,F"To the extent the arguments that are
OL,13,Fmade about human rights, and freedom
OL,14,Fof conscience, speech, and assembly,
OL,15,Fhave been considered by the Supreme
OL,16,FCourt, and we say that's a binding
OL,17,Fdecision on this court," said the
OL,18,Fprosecutor.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@RO]tD@AOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FMr McNeill argued that Mr Johnston had
OL,7,Fchosen to conduct his service at that
OL,8,Fparticular point, because the clinic
OL,9,Fwas there and that "we say he would
OL,10,Fnever, in a month on Sundays or
OL,11,FWednesdays, or any other day, have
OL,12,Fbeen there," if not for the presence
OL,13,Fof the clinic.
OL,15,FHe revealed that according to the
OL,16,Fskeleton argument on behalf of the
OL,17,Fdefendant, that he "could not form the
OL,18,Fmental element because he was acting
OL,19,Fas a channel for God's sovereign
OL,20,Fchoice."
OL,26,@qD@TOUtD@LO]yD@TOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FProsecuting counsel contended however,
OL,7,Fthat whatever the theological
OL,8,Freasoning behind it, "that is not a
OL,9,Fviable prospect."
OL,11,F"The simple prosecution position is
OL,12,Fthis," he told Judge King, "the
OL,13,Fdefendant intended that his preaching,
OL,14,Fwhether with the aid of God's grace or
OL,15,Fnot, should have an effect (on anyone
OL,16,Fattending the clinic)."
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@QO]sD@AOUtD@FO]tD@\OUwD@\pmxD@
OL,26,AUpnxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FIn his submissions, defence KC John
OL,7,FLarkin said that an "unmistakeable"
OL,8,Felement of the legislation was that
OL,9,Fthe prosecution have to prove the
OL,10,F"existence of one or more protected
OL,11,Fpersons."
OL,13,F"This offence is meaningless unless
OL,14,Fthere is a protected person who is
OL,15,Fdoing something with a specified
OL,16,Fpurpose," he argued, "and the very
OL,17,Fgranularity of that, makes it quite
OL,18,Finconceivable that the offence could
OL,19,Fbe committed if the existence of a
OL,20,Fparticular protected person cannot be
OL,21,Festablished."
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@cO]rD@AOUsD@IO]uD@AOUxD@IO]xD@
OL,26,AVOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FHe highlighted that the prosecution
OL,7,Fhad not called "any evidence
OL,8,Fwhatsoever," that any person was
OL,9,Fattending the clinic when the
OL,10,Fdefendant "was teaching about the love
OL,11,Fof God."
OL,13,F"This is an attempt to interfere with
OL,14,Fgospel preaching. Gospel preaching was
OL,15,Fthe object, gospel preaching was the
OL,16,Fintention, and we say it is simply
OL,17,Fwrong to attempt to extend section 52
OL,18,Fin the way proposed by the
OL,19,Fprosecution," Mr Larkin declared.
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@LO]rD@KOUsD@HO]uD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776971469
OL,3,CJudgment reserved over retired pastor
OL,4,Caccused of illegal abortion protest
OL,6,FThanking Mr McNeill and Mr Larkin once
OL,7,Fagain, Judge King said he would be
OL,8,Fdelivering a written judgement "of
OL,9,Fsome length," given the issues raised
OL,10,Fin the case and the fact the case
OL,11,Fcould be referred to higher courts.
OL,13,FThe case was adjourned to 7 May.
